parameters: **A mysterious voice speaks**
It is now time for your final test. You must prove
yourself worthy by surviving this trial.
Beware, for if you answer incorrectly, you will need
to battle against the monsters residing in this world.
Now prove yourself of being worthy of achieving BAA
Mastery.
Since you have earned the Mastery Awards in Service,
Education, and Progress, you may bypass a few of the
challenges.
Unfortunately, it seems that you have not earned all
of the Mastery Awards, so the crystal barrier will not
be taken down.
You now must attempt all the challenges.
